# Contacting SPI

To contact SPI, please send email to one of the following:

* The SPI [mailing lists](mailinglists/)
* The [SPI Board of Directors](mailto:board@spi-inc.org)
* The [SPI Officers](mailto:officers@spi-inc.org)
(President, VP, Secretary, Treasurer)
* An individual [officer or board member](../corporate/board)
* For press/publicity related questions, please contact [press@spi-inc.org](mailto:press@spi-inc.org)
* For website related questions, please contact [webmaster@spi-inc.org](mailto:webmaster@spi-inc.org)
* For treasurer and sys admin related requests, please file a ticket in
our [RT ticketing system](../corporate/rt/).
* Follow or contact us on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/spi_inc)

You can send mail to SPI at:

	Software in the Public Interest, Inc.
	1632 1st Ave #20327
	New York, NY 10028
	United States

## Authorized Signers

Only the [officers of the organization](/corporate/by-laws) are allowed to sign
binding documents in SPI's behalf. Any document, email or act not in accordance
with [Resolution 2015-06-02.mm.1](/corporate/resolutions/2015/2015-06-02.mm.1/)
may be a void document.

If you need to validate if a document, email or act is legit (issued by SPI),
please contact the [SPI Officers](mailto:officers@spi-inc.org) email address.
